BEGIN_PGML

Report the values from the magnitude plot of the following transfer function.

>>[``H(s) =	\frac{s(s + [$zero])}{(s + [$pole])(s^2 + [$second_term]s + [$third_term])}``]<<

_Note: all zeros and poles are in units of rad/s__.

END_PGML

BEGIN_TEXT

$PAR
\{
